T1  - Note on “Guarantees in Auctions: The Auction House as Negotiator and Managerial Decision Maker”
AU  - Greenleaf, Eric A.
AU  - Ma, Jun.
AU  - Qiu, Wanhua.
AU  - Rao, Ambar G.
AU  - Sinha, Atanu R.
Y1  - 2002/12/01
